item.title: [HBASE-15670] Add missing Snapshot.proto to the maven profile for compiling protobuf
item.description:
We had to debug an issue that resulted in mis-generated protobuf code in backported patches. It turns out that Snapshot.proto is not in hbase-protocol/pom.xml which results in the corresponding java code to be skipped when you do: 


mvn compile -Pcompile-protobuf
item.summary: Add missing Snapshot.proto to the maven profile for compiling protobuf

status.description: A resolution has been taken, and it is awaiting verification by reporter. From here issues are either reopened, or are closed.

comments.comment:
Simple patch. Does some rename in the test protobufs.

Ted Yu do you mind a quick review.
